inlineContent.text: The Heads Up Mobile iOS SDK provides a structured, easy-to-use API for accessing the Heads Up Cloud platform. It contains a set of high level objects you can use to perform a variety of tasks, such as:
Log in or register with Heads Up’s cloud services using Single Sign On (SSO) or user id and password
Connect and disconnect user’s devices such as Oura, Dexcom, Fitbit, and so on
Retrieve health metric data from the Heads Up cloud for optional storage in a data lakehouse
Upload Apple HealthKit data to the cloud in both foreground and background modes
